description:
These lightweight and stretchy pants have technical features to suit hiking, road trips or travelling.  A gusseted crotch and knee darts give you room for stepping over logs or sprinting along train station platforms. Lots of pockets keep your camera and maps within reach and safely tucked away.Stretch nylon fabric is comfortable and durable in urban or backcountry environments.Fabric is quick-drying with a DWR finish.Belt loops.Articulated knees and gussetted crotch allow unrestricted movement.Jeans-like hand pockets and top stitched rear pockets.1 zippered and 1 envelope cargo pocket provide extra storage.

        Sustainability






